description: Your rusty high school chemistry class knowledge might not be enough to help you win an Au metal in this challenging quiz!  You'll need steely resolve to score enough for an Ag or a Bronze!  You'll need to be a modern alchemist to be pliable enough to mine a high score on this brazen test, which is designed with ironclad questions, to undermine your chance at the brass ring!
name: Periodic Table Quiz
shortDescription: Your rusty high school chemistry class knowledge might not be enough to help you win a Au metal in this challenging quiz about the Periodic Table!
